---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Onoranze Funebri FADI — Dasà (VV) | Dal 1991"
  description="L'Agenzia Funebre FADI opera a Dasà (VV) dal 1991. Servizi funebri completi, trasporti nazionali e internazionali, disponibilità H24. Chiama 0963 353321."
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <Hero />

  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <section class="section about-section" id="chi-siamo">
    <div class="container about-grid">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="section-label">Chi siamo</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Un'agenzia funebre al tuo fianco da oltre trent'anni</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p class="section-text">
          L'Agenzia Funebre FADI opera a Dasà (VV) ed in tutta Italia dal 1991, offrendo servizi
          funebri di alta qualità con automezzi propri, garantendo un servizio completo con tutto il
          supporto necessario — sia organizzativo che burocratico — per affrontare con lucidità e
          sicurezza un momento tanto delicato.
        </p>
        <p class="section-text" style="margin-top:1rem;">
          Il nostro obiettivo è fornire tutti i servizi necessari per soddisfare i desideri e le
          esigenze del committente, con trasparenza assoluta nel rapporto qualità/prezzo. Eroga i
          propri servizi presso cliniche, ospedali, case di cura e abitazioni.
        </p>
        <div class="about-stats">
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-number">30+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Anni di esperienza</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-number">H24</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Reperibilità continua</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-number">IT</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Trasporti nazionali</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-side">
        <div class="about-card">
          <div class="about-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">✝</div>
          <h3>Disponibilità continua</h3>
          <p>Giorno e notte, anche nei festivi. Siamo sempre al tuo fianco quando hai bisogno di noi.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-card">
          <div class="about-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">◈</div>
          <h3>Professionalità e discrezione</h3>
          <p>Ogni servizio è curato nei minimi dettagli, con rispetto e sensibilità verso le famiglie.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-card">
          <div class="about-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">◎</div>
          <h3>Automezzi propri</h3>
          <p>Trasporti funebri nazionali e internazionali con mezzi propri e personale specializzato.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICES GRID -->
  <section class="section services-section" id="servizi-home">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="services-header">
        <p class="section-label">I nostri servizi</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Tutto ciò di cui hai bisogno, in un unico posto</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="services-grid">
        <a href="/servizi" class="service-card" id="card-servizi">
          <div class="service-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/>
              <polyline points="9,22 9,12 15,12 15,22"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Servizi funebri</h3>
          <p>Funerali completi, vestizioni, servizi religiosi e disbrigo pratiche burocratiche.</p>
          <span class="service-card-link">Scopri →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/fioreria" class="service-card" id="card-fioreria">
          <div class="service-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M12 22V12M12 12C12 12 8 10 8 6a4 4 0 0 1 8 0c0 4-4 6-4 6z"/>
              <path d="M12 12c0 0-4-2-6-5.5A4 4 0 0 1 12 7"/>
              <path d="M12 12c0 0 4-2 6-5.5A4 4 0 0 0 12 7"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Fioreria</h3>
          <p>Composizioni floreali personalizzate, fiori e corone per onorare il ricordo del tuo caro.</p>
          <span class="service-card-link">Scopri →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/necrologi/" class="service-card service-card--gold" id="card-annunci">
          <div class="service-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/>
              <polyline points="14,2 14,8 20,8"/>
              <line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/>
              <line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/>
              <polyline points="10,9 9,9 8,9"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Annunci funebri</h3>
          <p>Consulta i necrologi e le dirette delle cerimonie funebri nella nostra area.</p>
          <span class="service-card-link">Vai agli annunci →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/contatti" class="service-card" id="card-contatti-home">
          <div class="service-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/>
              <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Contatti</h3>
          <p>Siamo a Dasà (VV). Contattaci per ricevere assistenza e informazioni in ogni momento.</p>
          <span class="service-card-link">Dove siamo →</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA STRIP -->
  <section class="cta-strip" aria-label="Chiamaci ora">
    <div class="container cta-inner">
      <div class="cta-text">
        <h2>Hai bisogno di assistenza immediata?</h2>
        <p>Siamo disponibili 24 ore su 24, 7 giorni su 7. Non esitare a contattarci.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cta-actions">
        <a href="tel:+390963353321" class="btn btn-gold" id="cta-tel-main">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6.62 10.79a15.05 15.05 0 0 0 6.59 6.59l2.2-2.2a1 1 0 0 1 1.01-.24c1.12.37 2.33.57 3.58.57a1 1 0 0 1 1 1V20a1 1 0 0 1-1 1C10.61 21 3 13.39 3 4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3.5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1c0 1.25.2 2.46.57 3.58a1 1 0 0 1-.24 1.01l-2.21 2.2z"/></svg>
          0963 353321
        </a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/+39328353321" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline" id="cta-contatti-link">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12.04 2C6.58 2 2.13 6.45 2.13 11.91c0 1.75.46 3.45 1.34 4.95L2 22l5.28-1.39a9.88 9.88 0 0 0 4.76 1.22h.01c5.46 0 9.91-4.45 9.91-9.91S17.5 2 12.04 2Zm5.77 14.18c-.24.68-1.41 1.3-1.97 1.34-.5.04-1.14.06-1.84-.11-.42-.1-.96-.31-1.65-.61-2.9-1.25-4.79-4.16-4.94-4.35-.14-.19-1.18-1.57-1.18-3 0-1.43.75-2.13 1.02-2.42.27-.29.59-.36.79-.36.19 0 .39 0 .56.01.18.01.42-.07.66.5.24.58.84 2 .91 2.14.07.15.12.32.02.51-.1.19-.15.31-.29.48-.15.17-.31.38-.44.51-.15.15-.3.31-.13.6.17.29.75 1.24 1.62 2.01 1.11.99 2.04 1.3 2.33 1.45.29.15.46.12.63-.07.17-.19.72-.84.92-1.13.19-.29.39-.24.66-.15.27.1 1.72.81 2.01.96.29.15.48.22.56.34.07.12.07.7-.17 1.38Z"/></svg>
          Scrivi un messaggio
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* ABOUT */
  .about-section {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 380px;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-stats {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(44, 38, 32, 0.02);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .stat-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gold);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .stat-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 40px;
    background: var(--border);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .about-side {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .about-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(44, 38, 32, 0.02);
    transition: border-color var(--transition), transform var(--transition), box-shadow var(--transition);
  }

  .about-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(184, 150, 110, 0.08);
  }

  .about-card-icon {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .about-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .about-card p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* SERVICES */
  .services-section {
    background: var(--bg-soft);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .services-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .service-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(44, 38, 32, 0.02);
    transition: border-color var(--transition), transform var(--transition), background var(--transition), box-shadow var(--transition);
  }

  .service-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    background: rgba(184,150,110,0.02);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(184, 150, 110, 0.1);
  }

  .service-card--gold {
    border-color: rgba(184,150,110,0.35);
    background: rgba(184, 150, 110, 0.04);
  }

  .service-card--gold:hover {
    background: rgba(184, 150, 110, 0.08);
  }

  .service-card-icon {
    color: var(--gold);
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    background: var(--gold-dim);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .service-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .service-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.65;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .service-card-link {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  /* CTA STRIP */
  .cta-strip {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(184,150,110,0.1) 0%, rgba(184,150,110,0.05) 100%);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 3rem 0;
  }

  .cta-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cta-text h2 {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .cta-text p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .cta-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .cta-inner {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .cta-actions {
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
